en Version:
Thank you for becoming a member of Chai Khana. We look forward to exploring the stories you build!

When you have a chance, please visit your settings page so you can update your avatar, nickname, personal URL, and a summary about yourself: [settings_link].

You can manage when you would like to receive email notifications from Chai Khana by going to the notifications page: [notifications_link].
az Translation:
Çayxananın üzvü olduğunuz üçün təşəkkür edirik. Sizin yaradacağınız hekayələri səbirsizliklə gözləyirik!

Lütfən, imkanınız olanda parametrlər səhifənizə daxil olun ki, avatarınızı, ləqəbinizi, şəxsi URL-ınızı, və özünüz barədə xülasəni yenilədə biləsiniz: [settings_link].

Bildiriş səhifəsinə gedərək, Çayxanadan aldığınız bildirişlərin vaxtını müəyyənləşdirə bilərsiniz: [notifications_link].

en Version: You can copy and share the following URL with whomever you want to review '%{title}' before it is published. These people will have the ability to read your story, but not edit it.

en Version: Heading of infographic will appear above the infographic image. If this Infographic Section is first in the story, you should leave this blank and use the Story Title field.
az Translation: Heading of infographic will appear above the infographic image. If this Infographic Section is first in the story, you should leave this blank and use the Story Title field.

en Version: The description will appear below the infographic. If this Infographic Section is first in the story, the Story Summary will appear below the infographic image so if the Story Summary and Infographic Description are the same, you should leave this field blank.
az Translation: The description will appear below the infographic. If this Infographic Section is first in the story, the Story Summary will appear below the infographic image so if the Story Summary and Infographic Description are the same, you should leave this field blank.

en Version: Only jpg and png format allowed; 8MB file size limit

en Version: Please try to compress files to make for quicker download; 25MB file size limit
az Translation: Please try to compress files to make for quicker download; 25MB file size limit

en Version: Static infographics are images, Dynamic infographics require a URL.
az Translation: Static infographics are images, Dynamic infographics require a URL.

en Version: URL to web page with interactive infographic
az Translation: URL to web page with interactive infographic

en Version: Use these fields to indicate the space you want to reserve for showing this infographic. Leave the fields empty if you want the infographic to be fullscreen. The minimum value is 200.
az Translation: Use these fields to indicate the space you want to reserve for showing this infographic. Leave the fields empty if you want the infographic to be fullscreen. The minimum value is 200.

en Version: The infographic can be rendered in the story or in a popup that appears after the user clicks on the infogaphic image in the story. Use the popup option if the infogaphic takes up the full screen or is very long.
az Translation: The infographic can be rendered in the story or in a popup that appears after the user clicks on the infogaphic image in the story. Use the popup option if the infogaphic takes up the full screen or is very long.

Chai Khana Users You Are Following

en Version: If you didn't request this, please ignore this email.
az Translation: Bunu tələb etmədinizsə, lütfən bu e-poçtuna əhəmiyyət verməyin.

az Translation: Yuxadıraki keçidə daxil olub yeni parol yaratmadan sizin parolunuz dəyişməyəcək.
